    },
    {
      "id": "left-content",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 72,
      "y": 195,
      "width": 230,
      "height": 250,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#4A4A4A",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a7",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 310008,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 410008,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1706659200000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "定位：schema-first\n\n优点：\n• 类型安全强\n• 工程化成熟\n• 常规业务 API 很稳\n\n缺点：\n• 强依赖 codegen\n• schema 一变就要重新生成\n• 动态 model / field / input 很别扭",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top"
    },
    {
      "id": "mid-content",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 392,
      "y": 195,
      "width": 225,
      "height": 250,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#4A4A4A",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a8",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 310009,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 410009,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1706659200000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "定位：code-first + 运行时拼装\n\n优点：\n• 动态 schema 最灵活\n• Schema -> Field -> Resolver 心智简单\n• 很适合 meta -> runtime schema\n\n缺点：\n• 类型安全弱\n• 手写定义啰嗦\n• 约束和配套要自己补",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top"
    },
    {
      "id": "right-content",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 712,
      "y": 195,
      "width": 225,
      "height": 250,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#4A4A4A",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a9",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 310010,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 410010,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1706659200000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "定位：标准 schema 绑定 resolver\n\n优点：\n• API 比较干净\n• 常规服务端体验不错\n• 适合稳定 schema\n\n缺点：\n• 仍偏静态 schema\n• 动态 relation / filter 一般\n• 对 runtime 帮助不如 graphql-go 直接",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top"
    },
    {
      "id": "decision-box",
      "type": "rectangle",
